Wizard- (5)
- At night, the Wizard can perform a ritual spell on a respawning players body, this results in their respawn progress being adjusted by 2 phases. The Wizard can choose whether the adjustment is addition or subtraction (can become a negative number).
- Cannot target players who are not respawning.
- Completing the ritual is a Post-night action. 2 phase cooldown.
- Respawns in 4 phases.
